#------------------------------------------------------------------------
# GIT IGNORE CONFIGURATION
#
# Purpose: Defines files and directories that should be excluded from
# version control. Organized by category for easy maintenance and
# understanding of what gets ignored and why.
#
# Note: Patterns are checked in order. More specific patterns should
# come after general ones. Use comments to explain non-obvious patterns.
#------------------------------------------------------------------------

